#
#   This entry is the Go=184 leader bump that continues Axis 129
#   (pure-Rust + pure-Go peer-to-peer networking taxonomy) at
#   2/0/0 following R1085 _nsh (Rust=184 OPENED via fluffypony/
#   nsh on n0-computer/iroh 0.97 + iroh-docs 0.97).  TS-Node=184
